Abstract: This paper proposes a new standard library pointer class type that allows `operator->` member access to be resolved against a list of specified interfaces. All of the features described in this paper have been implemented—*tested and working*—in a compiler up on **GodBolt**:<br>[https://godbolt.org/z/YETv6zdWj](https://godbolt.org/z/YETv6zdWj)
